Linux

Monitoring Simple Troubleshooting

Server Slow?
top---> Check CPU storage
High CPU usage
top-->find which process
memory issue?
free -h-->check RAM usage
Load high CPU normal?
iostat---->check disk issue
Disk Slow?
iostat---->check disk performance
Disk full?
df -h -->check space
which folder is large?
du -sh* -->find size
which process are running?
ps -ef---> list process
App not Working?
ss -tulpn --->check port/service
Network issue?
ping ---> check connectivity
App showing Error?
tail -f logfile --->check live log
find exact error?
grep error logfile--->seach error